---
By: Seneca
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 406
    Verse: 8
Tags:
  - Search/Look Within
---
The great blessings of mankind are within us, and within our reach; but we
shut our eyes and, like people in the dark, fall short of the very thing we
search for without finding it.
